# Feature PM (per-feature artifacts)
# Track planning artifacts (REQUEST/PRD/BLUEPRINT/tasks.sql/coverage.json/STATE.md);
# ignore large/regenerable per-task context bundles and operational journals.
features/*/journal.md
features/*/tasks/*/context.md
# Keep the documentation example fully checked in.
!features/example-pm-dryrun/journal.md
!features/example-pm-dryrun/tasks/*/context.md

